Skills.Name: No Blinking!
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies within 100 cm of ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Further shields DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> of skill user's ATK) for 15s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies within range, shields DMG if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: A Song for You
Skills.Description: Raises Speed of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Also raises DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s. Further increases Speed by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 15s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises Speed and DEF of all allies. Further increases Speed if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: Radiant Sword Dance
Skills.Description: Raises own Overheal by {0}% (Permanent). Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{1}%</color> of ATK. Further grants Invincibility for 5s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises own Overheal. Recovers HP of all allies, grants Invincibility if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Echoing Radiance
Skills.Description: Each time Debuff is inflicted on self, shields DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of all allies for 15s (CT 3s). Further cancels 3x Debuff effects. (CT 3s)
Skills.ShortDescription: Each time Debuff is inflicted on self, shields DMG of all allies, cancels Debuff effect(s)
